-height: 150%;\">老师</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">4.审核：医院根据报名材料对报名人员资格进行审核，社会化学员招收结合本院培训基地招生要求发布进入考核人员名单。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">社会化学员报名现场资格审核需携带下列材料：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">①</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">简历一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">②</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">身份证原件及复印件一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">③</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">近期正面免冠二寸照片</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">张。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">④</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">毕业证书及学位证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">⑤</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">英语、计算机等级考试合格证书原件及复印件一份。</span></p><p st